02:07:37,340 --> 02:07:38,454
Liyun!

981
02:07:39,090 --> 02:07:40,086
Liyun!

982
02:08:37,567 --> 02:08:39,023
Socorro!

983
02:08:39,818 --> 02:08:40,814
Médico!

984
02:09:05,094 --> 02:09:07,170
